===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[apus|ăpūs]]'' "[[martlet]], [[swallow]]", a kind of bird said to have no feet, hence from {{Gr.}} [[άπους]] "footless"

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia|Apus}}
'''Apus'''

#{{constellation}}: A [[constellation]] of the [[southern]] sky, said to resemble a [[bird of paradise]].

